            <additions>
              <p/>
              <list>
                <item xml:id="addition1" n="1">
                  <locus from="29b" to="30a"/>
                  <p>On foll. 29 b and 30 a we find the following colophon, partly metrical, written
                    by the scribe <persName>Daniel</persName>. </p>
                  <p>
                    <quote xml:lang="syr">ܒܒܵܥܘ ܐܘ ܐܒ̈ܗܝ ܘܐܚ̈ܝ ܘܪ̈ܒܢܝ ܡܛܠ ܚܘܒܐ ܡܫܻܝܚܳܝܳܐ ܨܲܠܘ ܥܠ
                      ܬܠܡܝܕܐ ܕܝܠܟܘܢ ܡܚܝ̣ܠܐ ܕܢܝܐܝܠ ܕܰܒܛܰܝܒܽܘ ܐܬܒ̣ܪܻܝ. ܏ܘܫ. ܨܲܠܘ ܥܠܝ ܕܐܚܪܝܢ ܥܠܝܟܘܢ
                      ܢܗܘ̣ܐ ܡܨ̇ܠܐ. ܕܗܐ ܥܕ ܩܠܝܠ ܒܗܰܘܰܬ݂݀ ܡ̈ܝ̣ܬ݂ܐ ܩܢܘܡܢ ܒ̇ܳܠܷܐ. ܛܘܒܘܗܝ ܠܐܝܢܐ ܕܒܗܢ ܥܠܡܐ
                      ܐܰܘܳܢ ܗܶܒ̈ܠܶܐ. ܠܐܘܨܪ ܢܦܫܗ ܡܢ ܟܘܬܡ̈ܬܐ ܠܐ ܢܗܸܐ ܡ̇ܳܠܷܐ. ܣܶܢ̣ܰܬ݀ ܐܚ̈ܐ ܗ̣ܝ ܗܝ
                      ܪܻܫ̣ܰܬ݀ ܟܠܗܘܢ ܥܰܘ̈ܠܷܐ. ܘܡܲܢ ܕܟܪܝܗ ܒܗ̇ ܡܢ ܨܡܪܬܐ ܠܐ ܡܶܬܕܰܠܶܐ:</quote>
                  </p>
                </item>
                <item xml:id="addition2" n="2">
                  <locus from="51b"/>
                  <p>The colophon, fol. 51 b, consists merely of the words </p>
                  <p>
                    <quote xml:lang="syr">ܒܚܘܒܐ ܨ̇ܠܘ ܕܵܘܝܐ ܕܟܬ݂ܒ</quote>
                  </p>
                </item>
                <item xml:id="addition3" n="3">
                  <locus from="30a"/>
                  <p>On fol. 30 a a reader named <persName>Paul</persName> has written these
                    words</p>
                  <p>
                    <quote xml:lang="syr"/>
                  </p>
                </item>
                <item xml:id="addition4" n="4">
                  <locus from="51b"/>
                  <p>On fol. 51 b, another reader, named <persName>John</persName>, has written,
                    partly in Syriac and partly in Arabic, but using the latter character
                    throughout:</p>
                  <p>
                    <quote xml:lang="syr">ܒܚܽܘܒܳܐ ܨܰܠܰܘ ܥܰܠ ܕܳܘܝܳܐ ܕܰܟܬܰܒ ܗܳܕܶܐ ܡܚܻܝܠܳܐ ܚܰܛܳܝܳܐ
                      ܝܽܘܚܰܢܳܢ</quote>
                  </p>
                </item>
                <item xml:id="addition5" n="5">
                  <locus from="1a"/>
                  <p>On fol. 1 a there are one or two sentences in Arabic and Karshūnī, with the
                    name of the writer, Jacob</p>
                  <p>
                    <quote xml:lang="syr">ܐܕܟܪܘܐ ܝܥܩܘܒ ܐܠܚܩܝܪ</quote>
                  </p>
                </item>
              </list>
            </additions>
